{"tid":1288733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[林鄭入黎] 我教你下一步點做","createTime":"2019-07-05T18:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T18:45:26.000Z","uid":268243,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a63f24e6d607bd89b33ea5823e9b581ec804158","tid":1288733,"uid":268243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">下台</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n妳已無力管治香港<br />\n請勿再用以前嘅招數打發市民<br />\n妳嘅説話已無公信力<br />\n請用<strong>行動</strong>支持妳願與市民同行嘅口號<br />\n否則不可能帶領香港前行<br />\n感謝妳2年嘅努力<br />\n但市民已表態<br />\n妳的願景與手段並不為廣大市民所認同<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>或許妳覺得香港沒有比妳更適合嘅人選當此重任<br />\n而未來政府施政舉步維艱<br />\n只有妳有能力帶領香港走出困局</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一切都已經太遲<br />\nYou have had your chance and you fucked up<br />\n請妳離任之前<br />\n成立<strong>獨立委員會</strong>調查警隊濫權<br />\n的確有部分示威者違法<br />\n但無理由示威者要承擔後果而警察就唔洗<br />\nDouble standard 如何服眾<br />\n<br />\n當局者迷<br />\n不要沉醉在妳嘅支持者嘅歡呼聲當中<br />\n做得妳個位 我唔係要見到一個出黎喊嘅特首<br />\n我要一個實事求是 解決問題嘅領袖<br />\n所以 請妳為香港未來着想<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下台</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"de489cca3aeea761beb2ce1ef5ffc04621e7b1d0","tid":1288733,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08f336b9